3) 安迪·福特" width="2160" height="2700" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/NME-ENGLISH-TEACHER-2-CREDIT-ANDY-FORD@2160x2700.jpg 2160w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/NME-ENGLISH-TEACHER-2-CREDIT-ANDY-FORD@2160x2700-400x500.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/NME-ENGLISH-TEACHER-2-CREDIT-ANDY-FORD@2160x2700-800x1000.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/NME-ENGLISH-TEACHER-2-CREDIT-ANDY-FORD@2160x2700-696x870.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/NME-ENGLISH-TEACHER-2-CREDIT-ANDY-FORD@2160x2700-1392x1740.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/NME-ENGLISH-TEACHER-2-CREDIT-ANDY-FORD@2160x2700-1068x1335.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2160px) 100vw, 2160px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3495804" class="wp-caption-text">图片来源：《NME》安迪·福特</figcaption></figure><p>在采访的其他地方，怀廷表示，一起创作新音乐的兴奋感“极大地”加强了乐队的联系。</p><p> “我觉得下一组歌曲将真正反映我们现在的处境，”他补充道。 “我们不想坐在一种声音中；一些听起来宏大的歌谣即将出现。我们有一点需要证明。”</p><p>英语老师将于本月晚些时候开始他们迄今为止最大的头条巡演。您可以<a href="https://www.ticketmaster.co.uk/english-teacher-tickets/artist/5371524?irgwc=1&amp;utm_source=2862475-NME%20Networks%20Media%20Limited&amp;utm_medium=affiliate&amp;utm_campaign=2862475&amp;awtrc=&amp;clickId=zdmQRZTfwxyNUAZWPp1MB0h4UkFWG2zlnThV0M0&amp;camefrom=CFC_BUYAT_2862475&amp;ircid=7559" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在这里找到所有演出日期并购买门票</a>。</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/listen-to-english-teachers-dynamic-new-single-nearly-daffodils-3510922">听英语老师充满活力的新单曲“Nearly Daffodils”的</a>帖子首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
